<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Description==
</div>


L'outil [[Image:Sketcher_CancelSketch.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CancelSketch/fr|Sketcher Annuler l'esquisse]] permet de quitter le mode d'édition de l'esquisse, d'annuler toutes les modifications et de fermer la [[Sketcher_Dialog/fr|boîte de dialogue de Sketcher]].

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Utilisation==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|Cancel}} button at the top of the Sketcher Dialog.
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_CancelSketch.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_CancelSketch|Cancel Editing]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → [[Image:Sketcher_CancelSketch.svg|16px]] Cancel Editing}} option from the menu.
# The Sketcher Dialog is closed.
</div>


